Describe the use of the src and controls attributes in the <video> element. ~The src attribute specifies the URL of the video file. Controls attributes in the video element specifies that video controls should be displayed. Video controls should include: Play.
Why is it important to have fallback content inside the <video> element? ~ so the content that is to be used when the external resource cannot be used,because it is of an unsupported format.
